txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Coarse furs from beasts to the north of Amon Raith. Deliver the items to Nathan Hodges at Amon Raith.
'I will make certain that Agnes puts these to good use. Thank you.'
'Agnes asked for these furs. She wants the fur to come from bears, but any coarse fur can be used to create blankets. You will need to go north to find beasts with coarse fur.'
Rangers of Esteld√≠n Task: Coarse Fur
Nathan Hodges, at Amon Raith, awaits the collection and delivery of coarse furs.
Deliver the coarse fur to Nathan Hodges at Amon Raith
You have accepted a task to deliver coarse furs to Nathan Hodges at Amon Raith in the North Downs. You can find the coarse furs on the beasts to the north of the ruin of Amon Raith.
Wanted: Coarse furs from beasts to the north of Amon Raith.
